{"tid":717561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港地真係唔可以當同事係朋友","createTime":"2018-06-26T06:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T06:36:43.000Z","uid":164242,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20b480a98841ade7f340a08e5fd4db6b723b0f12","tid":717561,"uid":164242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"當普通朋友都唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論你對人有幾好有幾真<br />\n都唔排除人地會係你背後向上級篤背脊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自問平時做野方面一向冇問題仲幾勤力盡責<br />\n但個人太率直太直言 唔撚識奶人鞋底<br />\n個senior 竟然聽其他同事一言兩言就話我點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明呢啲小事唔影響公司運作就話要炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n初入職場既真係出到去要謹記<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">啲女人真係恐怖<br />\n絕對唔可以係佢地面前講真心話</span></strong><br />\n即使佢地表現到好明白或認同<br />\n背後桶左你一刀 死左都唔知乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係寧願你做明顯啲唔gur我 等我提防下你<br />\n都好過我當你係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：已被啲八婆小人搞到冇得撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e35c353685b692ab7e0f5889355a4e1be99cd1c","tid":717561,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"男人咪又係差唔多<br />\n不過女人多啲噉解"},{"pid":"214a02e1e4421ca51ecf81e16290d3b1da652420","tid":717561,"uid":160095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"同埋好撚多玻璃心 少少野就覺得串佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ee1600870091388ca1bf8f84229afb495fdb59","tid":717561,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"其實咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb23fdaa91d35e3b62250e9a7ac54fea3060e6f5","tid":717561,"uid":164242,"